sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant API as SkyDeploy API
    participant Engine as Build Engine (Docker)
    participant Caddy as Reverse Proxy

    User->>API: POST /deploy (Git/ZIP/Prompt)
    API->>API: Verify Auth & Roles
    API->>API: (If AI) Construct Code Payload & Sanitize
    API->>API: Generate unique dynamic PORT
    API->>Engine: Run isolated container (--cap-drop, limits)
    Engine-->>API: Container ID returned
    API->>Caddy: Write to Caddyfile & Reload
    API->>User: Deployment Success & URL
